{"tid":846037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾7成學童書包超重！小二生孭22磅返學 家長：手推車都拉爛","createTime":"2018-10-03T06:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T13:58:38.000Z","uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"a38ec5c3a4a5fad742abb2065b616af48839997a","tid":846037,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:30:03.000Z","msg":"2018年10月02<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181002/large/1538470317_28ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538470317_28ca.jpg&h=cfda92cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181002/large/1538470253_658b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538470253_658b.jpg&h=949b8cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181002/large/1538470314_d559.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181002%2Flarge%2F1538470314_d559.jpg&h=906eb25b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民建聯家庭事務委員會今發佈「學童書包重量調查」，工作人員於9月至10月訪問了726名學生，發現有77%受訪學童書包過重，即書包重量超過學生體重十分之一，726個書包的平均重量為4.1公斤，即約9磅重。與往年同類調查比較，今年書包超重情況稍有改善，書包平均重量下跌0.8公斤，超重書包比率亦下跌6個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯今午於筲箕灣愛東邨擺街站，趁附近小學放學，替學童檢視書包重量。就讀小二的孿生兄弟蘇雋行和雋言把書包上磅，發現重量分別都接近10公斤(約22磅)，書包內擺放飯盒、餐盤、餐具、10多本教科書和練習簿。家長蘇太更特意拉手推車接放學，直言書包「差唔多成包米咁重」，連手推車都拉壞過，她解釋，因怕書包太重，長年累月影響兒子脊椎發育，故每逢上下課都會由家長代勞。蘇太稱最直接了當的減磅方法就是減功課量，「無辦法啦，真係樣樣都要帶」，慨嘆傳統學校教育模式，令學生無法避免要「百上加斤」。<br />\n<br />\n就讀小六的梁同學書包亦有7公斤重，她説往來學校和家中距離長達15分鐘，肩頸經常痠痛，需粘貼紓緩疲勞膠布。她指，每日都有執拾書包，更會反覆檢查兩次，亦已把聖經、音樂課本等不常用教材放置在課室抽屜，但奈何無助書包減磅。<br />\n<br />\n委員會主席鍾嘉敏指，雖然調查反映書包超重情況稍有改善，但不可掉以輕心，建議教育局資助學校就某些科目購買「共用課本」，並存於在學校，另在編制上課時間表時亦應盡量多連堂，減輕學生攜帶課本的數量。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181002/58748033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F58748033&d=MleP2A74iKeYqMitjt%2BqW3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=53de8988\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181002%2F58748033&h=9bc3d6cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181002/58748033</a>"},{"pid":"918f0db1d74d8d895561b4f34db0b0389b99688a","tid":846037,"uid":136186,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"擺櫃桶啦"},{"pid":"fde86afa36cf6b1754e30d9ddd06c3b0f7d6aea0","tid":846037,"uid":35014,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:36:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a564a2f01eeddba6ac92962ef2481e3ff98e8d81","tid":846037,"uid":62379,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"屌諗起我中學勁on9，唔比留書響櫃桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個書包次次都重到仆街"},{"pid":"ef6217ada1325299933ea43613b6b7d58d137a0e","tid":846037,"uid":89514,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:38:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"78ba142f2a751319324b1e2024c0d1a9dc744a5b","tid":846037,"uid":136186,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"a564a2f01eeddba6ac92962ef2481e3ff98e8d81","tid":846037,"uid":62379,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:36:40.000Z","msg":"屌諗起我中學勁on9，唔比留書響櫃桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個書包次次都重到仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:39:57.000Z","msg":"同佢講唔俾留簿喺教員室"},{"pid":"53688875118ea1c1998bf3e530977e8cbf93df44","tid":846037,"uid":107927,"like":22,"dislike":3,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:40:04.000Z","msg":"等睇哩D comment<br />\n我細個果陣都係咁啦, 而家D細路驕生慣養"},{"pid":"1cbdc926590b7ad3a90a66bb7fde370aa564a470","tid":846037,"uid":139700,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:42:04.000Z","msg":